OL,4,C#170,000 jailed
OL,6,FA Kent Police investigation
OL,7,Festablished that their money had been
OL,8,Ftransferred to a business called NEG
OL,9,FServices Ltd, based in Ocean Drive,
OL,10,FGillingham.
OL,12,FThe sole director was Kevin Pook and
OL,13,Fhe lived at the same address.
OL,15,FIt quickly became clear that NEG
OL,16,FServices was a shell company set up
OL,17,Ffor the purposes of crime, although
OL,18,FPook could initially not be traced as
OL,19,Fhe was believed to have moved to
OL,20,FPortugal.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
