OL,6,FHowever he returned to the UK on 10
OL,7,FJanuary 2024 and was arrested at
OL,8,FStansted Airport.
OL,10,FPook was charged with money laundering
OL,11,Fthe following day and later pleaded
OL,12,Fguilty at Maidstone Crown Court.
OL,14,FOn Monday 19 August he was sentenced
OL,15,Fto one year and eight months'
OL,16,Fimprisonment.
