OL,6,FInvestigating officer Detective
OL,7,FConstable Mark Newman said: "Kevin
OL,8,FPook claimed he knew nothing about the
OL,9,Foffences being committed and that he
OL,10,Fhad opened an account on behalf of
OL,11,Fothers who controlled everything that
OL,12,Fwent in and out.
OL,14,F"Even if that were true, he still
OL,15,Fplayed a significant role in an
OL,16,Finnocent couple losing vast quantities
OL,17,Fof money and we were able to prove
OL,18,Fthat he benefited personally.
