OL,6,F"This case sends an important message
OL,7,Fthat even people who carry out their
OL,8,Fresearch and are very careful with
OL,9,Ftheir money can still become victims
OL,10,Fof crime. Before investing, always be
OL,11,Fabsolutely certain that the contact
OL,12,Fdetails you are using are correct and
OL,13,Fthat your money is going where you
OL,14,Fintend it to go."
